UID:8333-1780743600-1780752600@hardtruth.com
SUMMARY:Smoke School With Dave White
DESCRIPTION:Kick off the season of Bourbon and BBQ  with an unforgettable evening of smoke\, flavor\, and bourbon at Hard Truth Distilling Co. Join Dave White\, Pit Master of Great White Smoke\, for a 90‑minute celebrity cooking demonstration that takes you step‑by‑step through the art of crafting a perfectly smoked pork butt.\n\n\n\nDuring this immersive demo\, Dave will walk guests through his smoking process\, share expert tips\, and bring BBQ techniques to life all while you enjoy a delicious meal inspired by the demonstration. Each guest will experience a guided tasting of our whiskey and receive a goodie bag with more information.\n\n\n\nWhether you’re a seasoned pit master\, a backyard BBQ enthusiast\, or looking for a memorable weekend experience\, this event dishes up great food\, great company\, and a laid‑back atmosphere at the distillery.\n\n\n\nCome hungry. Leave inspired.
URL:https://hardtruth.com/event/celebrity-cooking-class/
LOCATION:IN
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Hard Truth Distilling Co.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Halifax:20260606T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Halifax:20260606T210000
DTSTAMP:20260515T003410
