LAST-MODIFIED:20260414T160029Z
UID:8366-1780768800-1780779600@hardtruth.com
SUMMARY:Rumble On The Rocks | Round 1 Night 2
DESCRIPTION:ROUND 1 CONTINUES: RUMBLE ON THE ROCKS\nNight two is here—and a whole new lineup of bands is ready to take the stage and bring everything they’ve got.\nIf you missed night one\, this is your chance. If you were there\, you already know… this competition is no joke.\nThese bands are battling for a spot in the finals—and a shot at:$2\,500 + a performance at Amplify Nashville$1\,500 + a performance at Amplify Nashville\n\nNIGHT TWO FEATURES: \n\nHoney White\nBengebreakers\nKnollwood Kings\nSustayn\n46 Drifters\nSarah Barton and 2nd That**Order of performance is selected on the day of the event\, and is not reflected by the listing above**\n\nThis is a FAN-VOTED competition. You decide who moves on.\n\nVoting details:Ballots are $10Each ballot = votes for TWO bandsThe top two bands from the night advance to the finals\n\nExpect another night of high-energy\, fast-paced sets and nonstop music.\nBring your crew\, show up loud\, and back your favorite bands—every vote counts.\nNew night. New bands. Same stakes.
URL:https://hardtruth.com/event/rumble-on-the-rocks-round-1-night-2/
LOCATION:IN
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Hard Truth Distilling Co.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Halifax:20260612T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Halifax:20260612T203000
DTSTAMP:20260515T003410
CREATED:20260324T163932Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260514T142716Z
UID:8300-1781287200-1781296200@hardtruth.com
SUMMARY:Cask & Still Social
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an unforgettable evening at the distillery as we host our Cask & Still Social—an intimate night celebrating exceptional whiskey\, incredible food\, and great company.\nThis exclusive experience will feature tastings of standout Hard Truth spirits\, including our Amburana Blend Straight Bourbon and Double Oaked Rye\, thoughtfully paired with expertly crafted small bites. The evening’s culinary offerings will be led by celebrity chef Dave White of Great White Smoke\, serving bold\, whiskey‑friendly flavors designed to complement each pour.\n\nGuests will also enjoy a curated tasting experience highlighting limited and specialty offerings from Hard Truth\, showcasing the craftsmanship and innovation behind our distilling process.\nTicket holders will have the opportunity to purchase featured spirits and select limited‑release whiskeys\, some of which are available only at the distillery.\nConsider this evening a taste of what’s ahead as we build toward our Bourbon & BBQ Festival on July 18—a refined\, behind‑the‑scenes preview for true whiskey and barbecue lovers.\nRaise a glass\, savor the craftsmanship\, and experience Hard Truth like never before.
URL:https://hardtruth.com/event/cask-still-social-7/
LOCATION:IN
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Hard Truth Distilling Co.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Halifax:20260613T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Halifax:20260613T210000
DTSTAMP:20260515T003410
CREATED:20260414T142826Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260414T142905Z
UID:8368-1781373600-1781384400@hardtruth.com
SUMMARY:Rumble On The Rocks | Final Round
DESCRIPTION:It all comes down to this. \n\nThe top bands from Round 1 are back—two from Night One and two from Night Two—and they’re going head‑to‑head in the final showdown. \nWhat’s on the line: \n$2\,500 + a performance at Amplify Nashville\n$1\,500 + a performance at Amplify Nashville \nWinners are decided by YOU + the judges.\nFan votes and judges’ scores combine to crown the champions—and your vote truly counts. \nAdmission: $10\nYour $10 entry includes your official voting ballot\, so every ticket holder gets a say in who takes it all. \nExpect the best of the best: dialed‑in sets\, high stakes\, and a night that actually means something for these artists. \nBring your crew. Be loud. Cast your vote.\nFour bands. One stage. Two winners.
URL:https://hardtruth.com/event/rumble-on-the-rocks-finals/
LOCATION:IN
END:VEVENT
